msgctxt "QL_KnightDoll_Desc"
msgid ""
"There are statues of <1.se_co>the seven heroines <2.re_co>east of \n"
"Gerudo Town. They may have something to do\n"
"with the location of a hidden shrine.\n"
"\n"
"First, solve the meaning behind the message:\n"
"\"When the symbols of the seven find their place,\n"
"the blessed path will be revealed.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_KnightDoll_Finish"
msgid ""
"\"When the symbols of the seven find their place,\n"
"the blessed path will be revealed.\"\n"
"\n"
"The ancient shrine appeared after you matched\n"
"the symbols on the orbs with the symbols of the\n"
"seven heroines."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_KnightDoll_Name"
msgid "The Seven Heroines"
msgstr ""

